{"tid":1939850,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】大陸戲院被迫復工播舊片 高層抱怨：開了也沒生意","createTime":"2020-03-23T11:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T11:44:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d6295614f1c1df004abc955cf4ec3781c39eb9b","tid":1939850,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:26:04.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎在全球肆虐之際，大陸聲稱疫情已放緩，所以鼓勵民眾復工，又批准戲院重開。據大陸電影網站貓眼資料，上周五（20日）全國合共有486家影院復工，復工率4.28%，當日總票房僅得13,800元人民幣，而廣東38家影院、河南128家影院復工，票房都是0元。到上周六（21日）復工戲院上升至507間，全國當日票房31,000元人民幣，在「全國復工省份票房TOP5」中 ，廣東突破0收入，以55元票房打入第5位，慘不忍睹！<br />\n<br />\n票房差，其實與沒新片上映有很大關係。<br />\n北京某發行公司高層王總向《蘋果》爆料，政府為刺激經濟，不斷鼓勵戲院復工營業，但民眾根本不肯入場。同時又因為票房太低，電影公司根本不肯讓新片上映，現時戲院全部都播舊片，包括《戰狼2》、《流浪地球》、《狼圖騰》、《中國合夥人》和《葉問4》，對觀眾來說根本欠缺吸引力，網民都埋怨怎會冒險入場看一部舊片。王總表示：「我們北京的戲院為甚麼還是關門，是因為明知開了也沒生意，只要政府未強迫重開，我們寧願等疫情真正過去再復工，因為戲院開門做生意，每日開銷花一筆，如果沒客人，院商賠得更慘。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200323/large/1584958579_593d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200323%2Flarge%2F1584958579_593d.jpg&h=3f8260e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200323/ARGSQ3FSUECX4JAN4UPTOMFUFY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200323%2FARGSQ3FSUECX4JAN4UPTOMFUFY%2F&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr2WjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=441839fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200323%2FARGSQ3FSUECX4JAN4UPTOMFUFY%2F&h=2f77bc68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200323/ARGSQ3FSUECX4JAN4UPTOMFUFY/</a>"},{"pid":"9103f35eb231825c1049c5616bf2975a2d267e39","tid":1939850,"uid":245441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:27:52.000Z","msg":"好快就會有一車車人去戲院睇戲。"},{"pid":"ec1cf9a44e4985ecc96e4c9a37de4608792096d0","tid":1939850,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:35:16.000Z","msg":"遲早規定所有支那人每日最少入場睇一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294a5e4afed53c55fae15c83aac1e3615ce3e771","tid":1939850,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a824db8810139f6ae5e40694ed91c0aac58b3f3","tid":1939850,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:38:26.000Z","msg":"全國扮工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b337f6f0b59d6b03fb8c979c57b033729b103da7","tid":1939850,"uid":300139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:44:48.000Z","msg":"推多d優惠 鼓勵睇戲 鼓勵聚餐咪得 最好鼓勵班藍絲返去醫到變藍絲"}]}